      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SKY KING (3) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Bulli over 340m behind Pure Momentum (19.62) in a Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. WORTH A SHOT (6) recorded a 4 length third in a Maiden last time 18.17 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Worth following up. WINSOME TEARS (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Arctic Flash (18.14) in a Maiden. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Will give a great sight again. TICK TICK ZOOM (7) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
